title: Wage and Salary Disbursements, Distributive Industries, Services, and Government for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1929-1946 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. Data Are Monthly Totals At Annual Rate. Source: Survey Of Current Business, Supplement: National Income Division, 1954 Edition, Office Of Business Economics.
